{
  "stem": "888.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They made a selection of certain people, you understand, that they're going to send them here or there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they took you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, there was a-- later on, I found out that there was also over there a, you know-- what do you call it, where they got rid of people?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think they had a crematorium in Gross-Rosen also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But at that particular time, they killed so many people, that they-- which I figured out just, you know, afterwards-- that they needed people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They need to have bodies to send to these different camps where they made commitments to send so many people to work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's why they, they sometimes, you know, saved, you know, younger children when they know they didn't have no actually labor value.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we stayed a couple of days in Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they sent us to Bolkenhain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this Bolkenhain-- there was this lageralteste.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name was Wolf.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And actually, he was sent away from another camp because he was too cruel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know how they got rid of him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this-- he was near Dornhau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he came, you know, and he was a sadistic-- I mean, he was extremely sadistic, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This camp, we came in originally, I think, maybe 600, 700 people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a couple of thousand people who perished in that particular camp, in this little camp, in a period of about-- from, I think from, let's say, August, end of August, till February.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, for the first couple of weeks, we were-- they didn't know what to do with us, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, some-- even though they were young, there was a factory over there, a munition factory, you know, that they worked in.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
